WHO   — The Greater Will — the Outer God of golden Order
WHAT  — The distant Outer God behind the Golden Order — the power that raised the Erdtree and chose Marika as its vessel-god.
WHERE — ER · Elden Ring  Framework inputs: the Outer Gods beyond the Lands Between  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Everything golden in the Lands Between — the Erdtree, the Order, Marika's godhood — flows from its remote will.
HOW   — It governs through Order, grace, and the Two Fingers, having sent the Elden Beast to the Lands Between — yet it remains silent and unanswering.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  The gold that orders everything answers nothing.

